<div class="comments-head">Comments: Poor customer service at Expedia.com</div>


<div class="comments-body">
<p>Expedia customer support is the worst possible.  My story is too long to recant at this time (or too painful).  The short story is they left me on hold for at least 30 minutes.  Promised to call me back with alternative options to a "4" Star Hotel that was somewhere between 2 and 3.  Never called back.  When I called again to be reconnected to the "supervisor" that was to call me back.  The customer support person told me she had to check with her supervisor first, then put me on hold and left me there until I hung up 30 minutes later.</p>

<p>I will write a letter.... I expect no response.  The only worse customer support I have experienced is MCI!</p>
